      "body" : "The standard autotools-generated behavior is to create a tarball that does not include autogen.sh, and does include a fully prepared configure.  The build machine (executor of ./configure) is not typically required to have autotools.  autotools tries to minimize what dev tools are required. ```make distcheck``` tarballs do not include it.\r\n&lt;/general principle&gt;\r\n\r\nFeel free to deviate from the standard, if there is logic and downstream benefit...\r\n",
      "created_at" : "2014-09-30T21:00:58Z",
      "html_url" : "https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/4997#issuecomment-57382061",
      "id" : 57382061,
      "issue_url" : "https://api.github.com/repos/bitcoin/bitcoin/issues/4997",
